SECTION 1  General Parameters/Thread Pool
PUBLIC    
NAME       system.tpool.affinity
LEVEL      Basic
TITLE      CPU affinity
VALID      None
TYPE       String
REQUIRED   No
DYNAMIC    No
DEFAULT    
This parameter defines the process CPU affinity. Leave it blank to use all available cores, else specify here some numbers or ranges, separated by commas and without any white spaces. For example -> 0,5,7,9-11 (The first processor number is 0, and range limits are inclusive: 0-2 means the first, the second and the third processors will be mapped to the process).

